---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
const CALCOM = site.calcomUrl;
---
<BaseLayout>
  <main class="pg" data-slug="about">
<section class="pg-section" data-section="About Us">
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="k.1757_serene_relaxing_nature_very_slight_purple_hue_very_relax_f9c18564-0ba0-42a6-8e7c-27" width="1440" height="547" loading="lazy" />
  <h1 class="pg-h">About Us</h1>
  <h2 class="pg-h">The Menon MediSpa Difference</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">At Menon MediSpa, we believe that beauty is about feeling confident in your own skin. Since 2019, we've been Millburn's premier destination for transformative, non-surgical aesthetic treatments that enhance your natural beauty.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/35c774fbba6d.png" alt="Menon Office Staff (1).png" width="425" height="323" loading="lazy" />
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/contact">Have Any Questions? Give Us A Call!</a>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Picture of a Client Who Reviewed Us" width="46" height="50" loading="lazy" />
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Picture of a Client Who Reviewed Us" width="52" height="50" loading="lazy" />
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Picture of a Client Who Reviewed Us" width="52" height="50" loading="lazy" />
  <p class="pg-text">★★★★★</p>
  <p class="pg-text">100+ 5 Star Reviews</p>
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="Our Approach:">
  <h3 class="pg-h">Our Approach:</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">What sets us apart is our commitment to three core principles:</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Medical Excellence - Our team of licensed medical professionals brings clinical expertise to every treatment. Led by Dr. Aditi Menon, MD, we combine the precision of medical science with the artistry of aesthetics.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Cutting-Edge Technology - We invest in state-of-the-art equipment and advanced techniques that deliver superior results with minimal downtime. Our technology undergoes rigorous testing to ensure safety, comfort, and effectiveness.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Personalized Care - Your beauty journey is unique, which is why we begin with a comprehensive consultation to understand your goals. We design customized treatment plans that address your specific concerns and celebrate your individual beauty.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Our Commitment:</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">We continually research emerging trends and techniques in aesthetic medicine, introducing new treatments only after they've proven their efficacy and safety. This dedication to innovation means you'll always have access to the most effective solutions available.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">The Experience:</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">From the moment you walk through our doors, you'll feel the difference in our warm, discreet environment designed for your comfort. Our attentive staff ensures every visit leaves you feeling refreshed, rejuvenated, and ready to face the world with confidence.<br />Your journey to radiance begins here at Menon MediSpa, where science meets beauty, and expertise meets compassion.</p>
</section>

<section class="pg-section">
  <h5 class="pg-h">BRINGING OUT THE BEST IN YOU</h5>
  <p class="pg-text">Our mission is to ensure that when you visit Menon Medispa &amp; Wellness you will feel at home and leave looking and feeling better than when you came in.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/meet-the-team">MEET THE TEAM</a>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/2ef11e239ab9.jpg" alt="" width="481" height="480" loading="lazy" />
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="What Our Clients Say">
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="Untitled-4.png" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
  <h3 class="pg-h">What Our Clients Say</h3>
  <blockquote class="pg-quote">Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.</blockquote>
  <p class="pg-text">Alexa C.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="Social Proof (5 Star Google Reviews)" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" />
</section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
